X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:33:58.546 --> 00:34:00.376 A:middle
As you may know, your apps on

00:34:00.506 --> 00:34:01.966 A:middle
iOS are Sandbox.

00:34:02.816 --> 00:34:04.666 A:middle
The App Sandbox is a security

00:34:04.666 --> 00:34:07.286 A:middle
feature, whereas every app has

00:34:07.356 --> 00:34:09.426 A:middle
unrestricted access to documents

00:34:09.426 --> 00:34:12.126 A:middle
in its own app container, and by

00:34:12.126 --> 00:34:14.896 A:middle
default, access is restricted to

00:34:14.896 --> 00:34:16.775 A:middle
documents in other containers,

00:34:17.085 --> 00:34:18.735 A:middle
namely in other app containers

00:34:18.735 --> 00:34:20.196 A:middle
and in cloud service containers.

00:34:21.466 --> 00:34:23.636 A:middle
So, this is a security feature

00:34:23.906 --> 00:34:25.585 A:middle
that guarantees that other apps

00:34:25.585 --> 00:34:27.426 A:middle
and processes don't just go

00:34:27.426 --> 00:34:29.036 A:middle
snooping around in your app

00:34:29.036 --> 00:34:30.366 A:middle
container, accessing your

00:34:30.366 --> 00:34:31.016 A:middle
documents.

00:34:31.356 --> 00:34:33.166 A:middle
And, always make sure that if

00:34:33.166 --> 00:34:35.076 A:middle
they do access them, access

00:34:35.076 --> 00:34:37.815 A:middle
these documents, that is done

00:34:37.906 --> 00:34:39.126 A:middle
with user consent.

00:34:40.636 --> 00:34:43.916 A:middle
So, since access to documents in

00:34:43.916 --> 00:34:45.656 A:middle
other containers is restricted,

00:34:46.106 --> 00:34:48.065 A:middle
how can your app gain access to

00:34:48.065 --> 00:34:49.466 A:middle
these documents that your

00:34:49.466 --> 00:34:50.485 A:middle
customer has picked?

00:34:51.585 --> 00:34:53.666 A:middle
What we have to do, is to extend

00:34:53.666 --> 00:34:55.476 A:middle
our App Sandbox to include these

00:34:55.476 --> 00:34:56.065 A:middle
documents.

00:34:56.775 --> 00:34:59.246 A:middle
Here's again the URL returned by

00:34:59.246 --> 00:35:00.266 A:middle
the Browser or the Picker.

